LAYERS: 

In my last projects, i've used the architectural pattern MVC (Model - View - Controller), with help the Spring MVC.
- Model: Business logic (Service - Entity - Dao) 
- View: Jsp
- Controller: View Layer < -Controller -> Model Layer

TIERS: 
In at Globant training i made an web application where i used:
- Client tier: HTML5+JS with Websockets for the backend comunication.
- Backend tier: Java application with WebSocket API.
- Data base tier: MySQL

